message:
Last month was Human Trafficking Awareness Month and the SuperBowl. This is a time that the news, social media, events are flooded with information about trafficking. The sad truth is it happens everyday, 365 day a year. With all the information we need to take action. There are different ways to help, we would love to hear from you on how you are continuing the conversation about Human Trafficking. ⠀
#Education #Awareness. #Action #DoSomething #CreateChange
